Напишите любой user-story и соответствующий тест кейс для сайта https://openweathermap.org/

***user-story:

As a User, I want to visit the Main page, so that I can see default city at the top of the page.

Acceptance criteria:

Verify the city’s name is "London" and it's visible;
Verify the date, and it's like system date and it's visible.


***test case:

Precondition:
Navigate to Main page https://openweathermap.org/

Steps:

Find city's name
Verify the city's name
Find the date
Verify date

Expected results:

The city's name visible and matches expected text (OpenWeather)
The date visible and matches system date